						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">image&nbsp;stuff</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The image is mine. Anyone can do whatever they want with it.</p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span>The Prison ♥. -Big Brother</span></h2> </div> <hr /> <p>Let's try this again.</p> <p>Thanks to everyone who looked at this in its conception, including <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1565583998" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hotcoles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3997195&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1565583998" alt="HotColes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3997195)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hotcoles" >HotColes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gentlegifts" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4275201&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1565583998" alt="GentleGifts" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4275201)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gentlegifts" >GentleGifts</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1565583998" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span>. I very much appreciate it.</p> <hr /> <h4><span>Art</span></h4> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Memories</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">by&nbsp;ResearcherSheppard</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/526584173180485642/610326590228004875/1831.png" alt="1831.png" class="image" /> <p>More of Luke's stuff can be found <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/luke-s-artwork">here</a>.</p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> 
